le&yacute;kositleri&#328; we ESR derejesini kesgitlemek bilen&nbsp;<b>umumy
kliniki gan barlagy&nbsp;</b>ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
