</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>G&ouml;wreli a&yacute;allarda pe&#351;ew ulgamyny&#328;
&yacute;iti we dowamly kesellerini (sistit, pi&yacute;elonefrit) &yacute;ok
