mikroskopi&yacute;a bilen umumy pe&#351;ew der&#328;ewi&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gan toparyny we Rh faktoryny kesgitlemek&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:
