gatna&#351;ygy (INR), fibrinogen we ere&yacute;&auml;n fibrin-monomer
toplumlary (RFMK) &yacute;aly g&ouml;rkezijileri kesgitlemek bilen
koagulogramma g&ouml;wreli a&yacute;alda &ouml;s&uuml;&#351;i&#328; gan
d&ouml;remek t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;iligi.&nbsp;</span></p>

