</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>G&ouml;wreli a&yacute;aly&#328; we d&uuml;w&uuml;n&ccedil;egi&#328;
&yacute;agda&yacute;yna yzygiderli g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik etmek.</span></p>

