dikeltmek we gowula&#351;dyrmak</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;aga wagtyndan
&ouml;&#328; plasenta bozulmagy bilen dikeldi&#351; d&ouml;wri a&yacute;al
&uuml;&ccedil;in gaty kyn we stresli bolup biler, &#351;onu&#328;
&uuml;&ccedil;in psihologiki goldaw gerek.&nbsp;Wagtyndan &ouml;&#328;
b&auml;bekler d&uuml;n&yacute;&auml; inenden so&#328;, k&ouml;plen&ccedil;
intensiw lukman&ccedil;ylyk k&ouml;megini talap ed&yacute;&auml;rler we
k&auml;bir &yacute;agda&yacute;larda hassahanada uzak
saklan&yacute;ar.&nbsp;So&#328;ky g&ouml;wreliliklerde wagtyndan &ouml;&#328;
plasenta bozulmagyny&#328; d&ouml;remek &auml;htimallygyny azaltmak &uuml;&ccedil;in
a&yacute;al t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;ilik faktorlaryny azaltmak we wagtynda
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;an alamatlara &uuml;ns bermek
&uuml;&ccedil;in lukman bilen maslahatla&#351;malydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

