color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gemodinamiki durnuksyzlyga seb&auml;p bolup bil&yacute;&auml;n
en&auml;ni&#328; gany &yacute;itirilmegi, k&auml;mahal &#351;ok we /
&yacute;a-da damar damarlaryny&#328; &yacute;ygrylmagy bilen &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>D&uuml;w&uuml;n&ccedil;ege zeper &yacute;etmegi (mysal
&uuml;&ccedil;in, sindrom &yacute;a-da d&uuml;w&uuml;n&ccedil;egi&#328;
&ouml;l&uuml;mi) &yacute;a-da dowamly plasentany&#328; bozulmagy -
d&uuml;w&uuml;n&ccedil;egi&#328; ulalmagy &yacute;a-da oligohidramnios.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>D&uuml;w&uuml;n&ccedil;egi&#328; eneden gan akmagy we
alloimmunizasi&yacute;a (mysal &uuml;&ccedil;in, Rh du&yacute;gurlygy
seb&auml;pli).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351;
&ccedil;&auml;releri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>G&ouml;wreliligi&#328; irki
d&ouml;w&uuml;rlerinden ba&#351;lap, g&ouml;wreli a&yacute;alda adaty
&yacute;erle&#351;&yacute;&auml;n plasentany&#328; wagtyndan &ouml;&#328;
a&yacute;rylmagyna seb&auml;p bolup biljek t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;ilik
faktorlaryny kesgitlemeli.&nbsp;Bejergini&#328; netijeliligine
g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik etmek bilen birme&#328;ze&#351; keselleri we
kyn&ccedil;ylyklary d&uuml;&yacute;pli g&ouml;zden ge&ccedil;irmek we bejermek
ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Preeklampsi&yacute;aly g&ouml;wreli
a&yacute;allara a&yacute;ratyn &uuml;ns berilmelidir.&nbsp;Ambulatori&yacute;a
esasynda ge&ccedil;irilen bejergini&#328; t&auml;siri bolmadyk
&yacute;agda&yacute;ynda g&ouml;wreli a&yacute;aly &ccedil;aga dogrul&yacute;an
hassahanada &ouml;z wagtynda hassahana
